    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Aggregate multiple contract calls in a single tx, taking affiliate fees up front.\\nReturns the actual `output_token` balance delta for `user`.\\n\\n`swap_id` is a caller-supplied 16-byte identifier (e.g. UUIDv4) emitted in the\\n`swap` event so off-chain systems can correlate transactions.",
